                            <comment id="15311901" author="krummas" created="Thu, 2 Jun 2016 07:53:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/krummas/cassandra/commits/marcuse/intervaltreesstableset&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/krummas/cassandra/commits/marcuse/intervaltreesstableset&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/krummas/job/krummas-marcuse-intervaltreesstableset-testall/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://cassci.datastax.com/view/Dev/view/krummas/job/krummas-marcuse-intervaltreesstableset-testall/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
