&lt;p&gt;patch to remove the option to pick which SSTableSet you want returned, only LIVE sstables supported now. If you want canonical sstables within bounds you provide an IntervalTree built over those sstables.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also includes &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11886&quot; title=&quot;Streaming will miss sections for early opened sstables during compaction&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;CASSANDRA-11886&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;CASSANDRA-11886&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; so that part might change depending on review in that ticket&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
